title: Opie & Jim Norton NOV 10 2015 Tue.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton NOV 10 2015 Tue (03:17:22)


On Today's Show:

JIM FLORENTINE, TODD ROBBINS, KEVIN BRENNAN, DJ WHOO KID, BRUCE CAMPBELL.

Jim Florentine is with Opie and Jimmy. They talk about whales and elephants, Starbucks cups, and a college professor protesting something racial.

Magician Todd Robbins joins them. They talk about his story, he eats a lightbulb, they talk about other magicians, and he tells them about his TV show.

Comedian Kevin Brennan joins them. He tells stories about his life and family.

Whoo Kid joins them as Jimmy leaves and they talk about the way black people spend their money. Bruce Campbell joins them. They talk about some of Bruce's work with big fan Whoo Kid asking lots of questions
